longBusinessSummary: Kingfisher plc, together with its subsidiaries, supplies home improvement products and services primarily in the United Kingdom, Ireland, France, and internationally. The company also offers property investment, finance, digital, sourcing, and IT services. The company provides its products through various channels, such as online and others. Kingfisher plc was incorporated in 1982 and is headquartered in London, the United Kingdom.
